---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Details" description="Ceremony, reception, dress code, and everything you need to know for Jack and Jenna's wedding.">

  <div class="section section--wide">
    <h1 class="page-heading">Details</h1>

    <div class="details-grid">

      <div class="detail-block">
        <span class="detail-label">Ceremony</span>
        <h2 class="display detail-title">TBD</h2>
        <p>Date, time, and venue to be confirmed. Check back soon.</p>
        <p class="detail-meta">[Address · Santa Barbara / Camarillo area]</p>
        <a
          href="https://maps.google.com"
          class="detail-link"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Open in Google Maps &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-block">
        <span class="detail-label">Reception</span>
        <h2 class="display detail-title">Following immediately</h2>
        <p>The reception follows the ceremony at [venue to be confirmed]. Dinner, dancing, and a great evening ahead.</p>
        <p class="detail-meta">[Address]</p>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-block">
        <span class="detail-label">Dress Code</span>
        <h2 class="display detail-title">Garden Formal</h2>
        <p>
          Think flowy dresses, linen suits, and anything that photographs beautifully outdoors.
          The ceremony may be partially outside, so flats or block heels are smart.
        </p>
        <p>
          Avoid white, ivory, and champagne. Everything else is fair game.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-block">
        <span class="detail-label">Good to know</span>
        <h2 class="display detail-title">Open Bar</h2>
        <p>
          Yes, there is a full open bar at the reception. Wine, beer, cocktails, and non-alcoholic options.
          Please drink responsibly and arrange a ride if you need one.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-block">
        <span class="detail-label">Children</span>
        <h2 class="display detail-title">[TBD]</h2>
        <p>
          [Let guests know whether children are welcome. If the event is adults-only, say so
          here warmly and clearly. If kids are welcome, note it.]
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-block">
        <span class="detail-label">Questions?</span>
        <h2 class="display detail-title">Reach out</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about the day, contact
          [point person name] at
          <a href="mailto:contact@example.com" class="detail-link">[contact@example.com]</a>.
          Please don't message the couple directly in the weeks before the wedding.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.details-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 1px;
  background: oklch(from var(--blush) l c h / 0.3);
  border: 1px solid oklch(from var(--blush) l c h / 0.3);
  margin-top: var(--s-md);
}

.detail-block {
  background: var(--cream);
  padding: var(--s-lg) var(--s-md);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}

.detail-label {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
}

.detail-title {
  font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--accent);
  line-height: 1.15;
}

.detail-meta {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--muted);
}

.detail-link {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  text-decoration: underline;
  text-underline-offset: 3px;
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 0.25rem;
}

@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .details-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
